  • Classes in net.marfgamer.jraknet.client used by net.marfgamer.jraknet.client 
    Class and Description
    RakNetClient
    This class is used to connection to servers using the RakNet protocol
    RakNetClientListener
    This interface is used by the client to let the user know when specific events are triggered

    Note: Do NOT use Thread.sleep(long) in any of these methods, as it will cause the client to timeout!
    Warning
    Represents a warning sent from the client when it is afraid an error will occur but is not sure if it will or not
